channel.title: 508 Server cache help
channel.description:
Hello fellow moper(ians?) I was wondering if it is possible to load a 525 cache on a 508. I bought a clean 508 source and I want to add pvp armors and such, and I was wondering how that would be possible? I did check the forums and many other places, but everything is not so specific. Thanks!
Source: 508 RS2hd original source, it was edited to clean it up and performance.
